[Weapon Attribute Digits\-]
author=nobody
description=0001 - Fire
0002 - Ice
0004 - Bolt
0008 - Flash
0010 - Slay
0020 - Quake? (that&#039;s what people call it)
0040 - Drain
0080 - Absorb
0100 - Air
0200 - Brave
0400 - Range
0800 - Multi
1000 - Agility
2000 - Might
4000 - Rage
7FFF - All of them

