[All Characters' Weapon 1 Has All Skills, 15 Slots, And +20 Extra Attack]
author=bungholio
description=That might freeze the game. I checked my weapon with all skills and the game froze, but I didn&#039;t actually try to play the game with it on. If the game freezes, you&#039;ll need to change the 7fff part. These are skills digits.
0001 Guile
0002 Iron Will
0004 Acrobatics
0008 Nutrition
0010 Firepower
0020 Verity
0040 Teamwork
0080 Evasion
0100 Stability
0200 Highflier
0400 Resolve
0800 Synergy
1000 Supremacy
2000 Revival
4000 Almighty
patch=1,EE,4052C26C,extended,005C0036
patch=1,EE,107F6142,extended,C72F4BD9

