[In-Battle Codes\Attack Damage Modifier]
author=bungholio
description=Change &quot;7fff&quot; to whatever you want. That value gives you nearly a 1-hit kill on every enemy on chaos diffculty.  It works for every attack you do.  Orochi X on Chaos difficulty takes less than 5 hits to kill. It also affects attacks you do while you are on a horse, except for the horse tackle below.  Works in every game mode.
patch=1,EE,1054194A,extended,00007FFF

[In-Battle Codes\Attack Range Modifier]
author=bungholio
description=Change &quot;4500&quot; to whatever you want. Some characters don&#039;t have any range. For example, Kotaro Fuma never has any range.  You can hit very far with &quot;7fff&quot;, and you will hit everything with &quot;ffff&quot;.
patch=1,EE,10541962,extended,00004500

[In-Battle Codes\Can Always Do True Musou Attacks]
