[In-Battle Codes\Horse Speed Modifier]
author=bungholio
description=Change &quot;4280&quot; to whatever you want. Works the same as the other speed modifier.  Only works while riding a horse.
patch=1,EE,10541966,extended,00004280

[In-Battle Codes\Horse Tackle Power Modifier]
author=bungholio
description=Change &quot;7fff&quot; to whatever you want. That value gives you a 1 hit kill on everyone you run over while riding a horse.  Even Orochi X dies from it on chaos difficulty.
patch=1,EE,1054194E,extended,00007FFF

[In-Battle Codes\Jump Height Modifier]
author=bungholio
description=Change &quot;4280&quot; to whatever you want. You can use it to jump over some gates, but jump over the walls, not the actual gates.
patch=1,EE,10541956,extended,00004280

