description=Change &quot;4280&quot; to whatever you want. You will run very fast.  I wouldn&#039;t reccommend going higher than &quot;4400&quot;, you&#039;ll move so fast you can&#039;t control it, you can move so fast you will go through things.  It doesn&#039;t affect your speed while riding on a horse.
